        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer844955030" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16586724126928893460">Although a little dated, a jewel of a piece about two people in love, outside of a traditional relationship. I really enjoyed the evolution of each character as they aged, and found myself invested in their growth together, as humans, as a couple, as individuals who come to know themselves, and each other so well. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


