    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3027716102" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11063457762272596392">Second time re read of this old beautiful play. I love this story. An unconventional love story, a lifetime affair they don’t try to explain. No justification. No apologies. They just enjoy the absolute present. Once a year, every year. Such a reminder that love is energy that binds and isn’t easily broken. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


