<div id="review_1066704725" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1066704725" />
    <a title="Urszula" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/13139368-urszula"><img alt="Urszula" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/f_50x66-6a03a5c12233c941481992b82eea8d23.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1066704725?book_show_action=true">Sep 28, 2014</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Urszula" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Urszula" href="/user/show/13139368-urszula">Urszula</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780440177586" href="/book/show/177005.Same_Time_Next_Year">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1066704725" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12119116020959065129">Truly believable romance. Great sense of humor. I have watched the movie tens of times, but reading it I could imagine George and Doris on my own. The dialogues are hilarious. I kept thinking, it could have happen to me, the story is so real. Great perspective on the past decades and what the times were like. Growing old, changing and staying the same at the same time. I will never get bored with this play! </span>

          </span>
        </div>


